RE=shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual, K=112, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 可 instantiate、forward、backward。","本地成本自检：selection_accesses=1499136、deployment_accesses=458752、combined_accesses=1957888，对 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.47，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束，也左于 r146 matched recipe 的约 0.54x。","最近三条 fresh 结构对照结果分别是 r147 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` FVU=0.1038、r148 `two_stage_residual_expert` FVU=0.1140、r149 `factorized_expert_topk` FVU=0.2450；因此继续在这些已有 family 上做局部扫参的信息增量很低，本轮更适合补最小新原型。"],"reference_round":146,"self_review":"这轮选择 `edit_sae_code` 而不是再做现有 family 的 param-only probe，原因是当前已连续三轮 fresh 结构对照都未形成新非支配点，而提示明确要求在这种情况下优先切换到新的结构假设或新增最小可运行原型。新 family 不是无约束扩张：它直接填补了当前最缺的“shared experts + routed experts + expert-internal low-rank + residual cleanup”槽位，并且只复用现有 tunable 参数，没有新增 env key。风险在于 residual_encoder 仍然较重，可能重复 r147 的结论；但这次 factorized stage 把 stage1 selection 从约 0.44x 压到约 0.36x，足以提供新的结构信息。","summary":"已新增并接线 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual`，建议以 r146 为 reference，仅设置 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual` 启动首轮真实训练。它是一个已落盘、已 smoke、已过 allowlist 的最小新 family，目标是在当前最需要补证据的 0.3x-0.5x 带直接回答“hetero MoE 的 factorized shared+routed stage 加 residual cleanup”是否值得继续。","touched_files":["research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py","sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"]}
